                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1" defective="false">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus/>
                        <div style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt;"
                             org="uniform"
                             sample="complete">Fol. 162rab: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ተፈጸመት፡ በዘመነ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ወበመንግሥተ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ኢያሱ፡ በ፸፻፡ ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፡ በ፩፻፸፡ ወ፯፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ በ፲ወ፪፡ አበቅቴ፡ በ፲ወ፰፡ መጥቅዕ፡ በ፲ወ፱፡ ሠርቀ፡ ሌሊት፡ እም፭፡ ሠርቀ፡ መዓልት፡ በወርኀ፡ ኅዳር፨  ለጸሐፊ፥ ወለዘአጽሐፊ፥ ለአንባቢ፥ ወለተርጓሚ፥ ለስማዒ፥ ወለለባዊ፥ ኅቡረ፡ ይምሐሮሙ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወያብኦሙ፡ መንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፨ አሜን፡ ወአሜን፨ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን፨</div>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en">
                           <div style="line-height: normal;" org="uniform" sample="complete">Fol. 162rab: This book was completed in the year of St. John the Evangelist and in the reign of our King ˀIyasu, in the year of the world 7000, in the year of mercy 176, the 12<sup>th</sup> epact, the 18<sup>th</sup> mäṭqəˁ, in the 19<sup>th</sup> night, from the 5<sup>th</sup> day in the month of Ḫədar…</div>
                        </foreign>
                        <note>Date meant is probably 7176 "year of the world" (separated into two dates according to two eras, cp. QSM-007), i.e., in 1684 A.D. (cp. Ms. MAKM-091, 1664 A.D.), during the reign of King ʾIyasu I (r. 1682-1706).</note>
                     </colophon>
